content.value: This roomy, everyday tote carries everything you need to conquer your day with confidence. This tote offers the perfect blend of lightweight and structured.
Size: 19.25" W (top) x 16.5" W (bottom) x 13.25" H x 3.75" D. 1.6 lbs empty.
Shoulder strap: double reinforced top handles with a 9.25" inch drop, the perfect length for throwing over your shoulder
Materials: 100% Saffiano embossed leather. Unlined interior in polished leather.
Interior: features a small interior pocket - 8” W x 6.25” H
Origin: made in Foshan, China
When dirty, give it a quick wipe with a soft dry cloth; with it you can use some leather cleansing cream or a small amount of water; let water spills dry naturally
